28 March 2017The African National Congress mourns the passing of Isithwalandwe/Seaparankoe, Comrade Ahmed Mohamed Kathrada who passed on earlier today, 28 March 2017.Members and supporters of the ANC, the Alliance, MDM formations and South Africans at large, are invited to sign a condolence book in honor of Comrade Kathy which will be placed at the ANC's Headquarters.The condolence book will be available at Chief Albert Luthuli House, 54 Pixley Seme Street, Johannesburg from 14h00 this afternoon.Issued by the African National CongressEnquiries Zizi Kodwa 082 330 4910 National SpokespersonKhusela Sangoni 072 854 5707 National Communications Manager